column1: ## comments and empty lines in this file are ignored.
## Two columns (space or tab-delimited) specify the barcode id and the bardcode itself.
## A lower case letter in the barcode means: this letter must *always* be exact.
## This can be used if some barcodes are not different enough from the other
## to allow a fixed number of mismatches.
## The current version fixes problems with insufficient edit distance in the previous versions,
## and is safe to use while allowing for a one nucleotide mismatch.
